Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:45.02,Line JP,,0,0,0,,あの…
Comment: 1,0:16:44.47,0:16:45.02,Line CN,,0,0,0,,ん？
Comment: 0,0:16:44.47,0:16:45.02,Line JP,,0,0,0,,ん？
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.65,0:16:47.62,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你先走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:47.62,Line JP,,0,0,0,,先に行って
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.28,0:16:51.57,Line CN,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:51.57,Line JP,,0,0,0,,んっ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.80,0:16:59.74,Line CN,,0,0,0,,啊  好  乖乖乖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:59.74,Line JP,,0,0,0,,あっ！　あ～  よしよしよしよし
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.74,0:17:02.10,Line CN,,0,0,0,,哇  噢  乖乖乖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:02.10,Line JP,,0,0,0,,お～  お～  よしよしよしよし
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.10,0:17:05.85,Line CN,,0,0,0,,嘿  有没有什么地方痒？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.10,0:17:05.85,Line JP,,0,0,0,,あ～  そらっ！かゆいとこはないかねえ？
Comment: 1,0:17:05.25,0:17:07.78,Line CN,,0,0,0,,あ～  ハハハハ
Comment: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:07.78,Line JP,,0,0,0,,あ～  ハハハハ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.78,0:17:10.05,Line CN,,0,0,0,,乖乖乖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:10.05,Line JP,,0,0,0,,よしよしよしよし
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.12,0:17:15.59,Line CN,,0,0,0,,乖乖乖  真是乖狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:15.59,Line JP,,0,0,0,,よーしよしよし  よしよし
